Scope: Looking west on King St. W., from just east of Simcoe St., one can see the Aladdin Building, St. Andrew's Church, the Canadian General Electric building and the Canadian Pacific Railway building. The new Canadian Bank of Commerce building can be seen in the distance, just going up.
